  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\nAvoid confusing users of ERC777\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\n\r\nThe ERC777 token contract implementation includes the _beforeTokenTransfer hook \r\n\r\nfunction _beforeTokenTransfer(address operator, address from, address to, uint256 tokenId) internal virtual { }\r\n\r\nThe last parameter is not a tokenId but an amount, still uint256 but misleading none the less, looks like a remnant from the ERC721 Token...\r\n\r\nAlso the calling conditions comments reference tokenId, and need to be updated\r\n",
